column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "984BD1864FFDD2DD00C45F8A6987CADB", "You again! Get out of here!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "DCA9E63F4D1EBC1C3A00E49FAF442534", "You... you\'re a pest! Is that okay now?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "B0F9C8B749308E2C8D07E5BE11E30A92", "You again! Get out of here right now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "3B2A83C642909F0627B4DDA5B303DCC4", "Did you come for something?")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "30940DA74089266630B8768013CC04F4", "If you have a request, forget it. Because I am KingSukamon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "4FF7C8714A02FD394C3F8F93F01910BE", "I guess I won\'t be able to invite him to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "D0DFEE9F4C496D56D6A908B980376681", "Good to see you, my friends. If you want to live here, I give you permission.")

column13: ((18, NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "D4DA51834CBB9E75A073FBADECBF2A53", "We want to live here")),(22, NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "7162E3024D27DE2DCF12288979166B71", "We want to return")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "928B9CE5456ADEC9F5FE0D98F5431D3F", "Hmmm, that\'s good. What? But you are analog, so you can\'t live here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "D6ADC331410E76A99D79D49517581204", "We have to be together!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "184AD35A4161FA3F89058DB80A97703B", "Then, get out of here with him!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "4EBC448243B2E52ED33EDF87DEE6CB3F", "What? What are you saying?")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "39EAD07B4776C43FAF2CC5AC349F4F53", "He\'s not originally Sukamon. King, please return him to his original form!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "4D17887F46C850B8F4B7839149CCD96A", "Isn\'t it great that he became Sukamon?")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "F6CDC95649075548E6F2AA8BE19C95F6", "No, it\'s not very good right now. Please.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "52E429394645E470260FFE858861D561", "Only way to become Sukamon is to try hard.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "74819E7D415947B5B6A9198E97509F5E", "He became a Sukamon naturally and that\'s the problem.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "BB0F3F7B494F4233F93A469666BC6ADB", "You guys are unbelievable!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "067930F24C162EA808059E8DD39FA2D0", "Wow! King, thank you!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BC450559460F7F856A0EFBAD21F47E43]", "7D11A68D4E63AC224F835DA15CAAFA83", "Get out of here right now!")
